            "title": "碧桂園重組倡部分發新股抵償  140億美元境外債 澳門大豐銀行設暫緩期",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"碧桂園重組倡部分發新股抵償 140億美元境外債 澳門大豐銀行設暫緩期\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iXEgxwdaFLARgUxPlSW2jw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-01/890a5900-bf36-11ee-9799-3523f22ded6a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">碧桂園重組倡部分發新股抵償 140億美元境外債 澳門大豐銀行設暫緩期</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
